## Description {#details}

Garbage collection metadata for a single function.

Currently, this information only applies to GCStrategies which use <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/gcroot">GCRoot</a>.

Definition at line 78 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/gcmetadata-h">GCMetadata.h</a>.
